s to c  adhering to the microsoftnet framework methodology while using the progressive abilities of net framework  such as parallel programming dynamic types etc access to databases access to databases will be done using the object relational mapping orm layer which enables data coupling between the data model – as is declared in the database  and its representation in the application additionally orm enables flexibility in choosing the database provider oracle microsoft sql server etc application security the application security in the new code is based on standard mechanisms available in the net framework an authentication mechanism for user identification will be implemented using formswindows authentication depending on the system environment additionally a role based security mechanism will be implemented in relevant places to create authorizations based on users and groups this mechanism is usually executed using standard membership provider unless the client requests otherwise download full product information friends email message httpsgouptecommagicsoftwaremigration send magic software enterprises shoppingnet top category matches  miscellaneous software  computer books  miscellaneous office  sc  miscellaneous  computer gaming software  learning toys  video games  bridges  routers  multimedia software  sort  stack toys  scanners  miscellaneous musical instrum  miscellaneous storage periphe  technology books  scifi dvds  videos  playsets  figures  building sets  models  weather instruments see all categories price price must be rounded to nearest dollar  to  free shipping video output type dvi   more genre action adventure  puzzle  more color black  blue  white  yellow  red  purple  more modem type analog  more networking type ethernet  fast ethernet  more publisher storm  nintendo  titus  more networking connection type ethernet  gigabit ethernet  usb  fast ethernet  ieee af  ieee   usb   ieee x  more switching protocol ethernet  more boot standard  more me