 company grew based on its sales to the dos and unix platforms the product was used by many large organizations including the israel defense forces in  the company changed its name to magic software enterprises retaining the acronym mse and became the first israeli software company to go public on the nasdaq during this period the company developed a close relationship with ibm focusing on as systems in mid the first version of magic for windows was released in  magic was acquired by the formula group headed by dan goldstein in february  it raised over  million and traded at a company valuation of  billion in  magic released edeveloper rohan a graphical rulesbased and eventdriven framework that offered a precompiled engine for database business tasks and a wide variety of generic runtime services and functions in february  menachem hasfari replaced jack dunitz as ceo after a series of failures that led the company to post two successive profit warnings in  guy bernstein was appointed chairman of the board at magic software enterprises replacing david assia prior to that bernstein had served as chief financial and operations officer of magic software since  guy bernstein was appointed ceo of magic software enterprises in april  in  magic released the ibolt integration platform in july  it released the first version of the unipaas application platform replacing edeveloper in  magic released a net version of unipaas and launched a new offering for enterprise mobility in may  magic launched a companywide rebranding including new product names a new logo and tagline unipaas was renamed magic xpa application platform and ibolt was renamed magic xpi integration platform the magic xpi integration platform was enhanced to include inmemory data grid imdg technology from gigaspaces in  magic entered into an agreement to acquire a  equity interest in roshtov software industries for  million with an option to acquire  of the equity in roshtov developer of the clicks platform used in patientfile oriented software solutions for managed care and healthcare providers see alsoedit economy of israel referencesedit  magic announces distribution of cash dividend for first half of  the wall street transcript   a b morgenstern henry  september  the magic continuesprogrammingfree program from magic software enterprises ltd israel business today – via highbeam subscription required retrieved  august    holloway simon  july  the magic story bloor research international retrieved    magic loses its illusions  magic software announces guy bernstein to replace david assia as chairman of the board formulasystemscom november    branding onlinefocused rebranding increases website traffic  facebook fans  youtube subscribers  marketing sherpa december    magic goes inmemory with app framework the four hundred july    magic software enters deal to buy  stake in israelbased roshtov software for  mln retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlemagicsoftwareenterprisesoldid categories software companies of israelhidden categories subscription required using viapages containing links to subscriptiononly contentpages using deprecated image syntax navigation menu personal tools not logged intalkcontributionscreate accountlog in namespaces article talk variants views read edit view history more search navigation main pagecontentsfeatured contentcurrent eventsrandom articledonate to wikipediawikipedia store interaction helpabout wikipediacommunity portalrecent changescontact page tools what links hererelated changesupload filespecial pagespermanent linkpage informationwikidata itemcite this page printexport create a bookdownload as pdfprintable version languages deutschfrançaisעברית edit links this page was last edited on  february  at  text is available under the creative commons attributionsharealike license additional terms may apply by using this site you agree to the terms of use and privacy policy wikipedia® is a registered trademark of the wikimedia foundati